Expository Graphs
  - graphs used to communicate results to other people

Characteristics:
  - communicate information
  - information density is good
  - color, size, and other aesthetics used to present info
  - proper labels

-- multiple panels per plot
par(mfrow=c(1, 2))  1 row, 2 cols


-- saving figures
?Devices

pdf(file="...", height, width)  dimensions in inches
...
..   graph commands
..
dev.off()


png(file="", height, width) dimensions in pixels

dev.copy2pdf(filename); -- directly copy the graph on screen to a file